  <brief_title>Effect of NT-proBNP Guided Treatment of Chronic Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Pro-brain-natriuretic Peptide Guided Therapy of Chronic Heart Failure Improve Heart Failure Morbidity and Mortality?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
