  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether NT-proBNP guided treatment of chronic
      congestive heart failure will reduce heart failure related morbidity and mortality compared
      to therapy guided by standard clinical judgement.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
